Class OrgSettingsType

java.lang.Object
  com.vmware.vcloud.api.rest.schema_v1_0.VCloudExtensibleType
      com.vmware.vcloud.api.rest.schema_v1_0.OrgSettingsType

public class OrgSettingsType
extends VCloudExtensibleType

Describes various settings for some organization. This type establishes quotas and policies for the organization. It also contains elements that specify the details of how the organization connects to LDAP and email services.

Java class for OrgSettingsType complex type.
